---
/**
 * Vibe Page — Layer 1
 * Connection page. What conversations interest me. How to reach me.
 */
import "../styles/global.css";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import TamilRoot from "../components/TamilRoot.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Vibe | Naveen Riaz</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Let's connect. Conversations about living systems, cognitive architecture, and Tamil wisdom."
    />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Vibe | Naveen Riaz" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Let's connect. Conversations about living systems, cognitive architecture, and Tamil wisdom." />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://naveenriaz.com/og-image.png" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://naveenriaz.com/vibe/" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  </head>
  <body class="section-vibe">
    <Header activeNav="vibe" />

    <main class="container container--narrow">
      <section class="page-hero section">
        <h1>Vibe</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Let's connect.</p>
        <p>
          Every engagement starts the same way: a conversation.<br />
          I am most alive when exploring ideas with people who care about depth over
          speed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section--tight">
        <h2>Atoms <span class="layer-label">The Vibe</span></h2><br />
        <div class="topic-list">
          <div class="topic-item" style="display: block; opacity: 0.7;">
            <p class="knots-badge" style="color: var(--vibe-color);">SHORT FORM</p>
            <strong style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              Syncs <span class="knots-badge" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--text-muted);">COMING SOON</span>
            </strong>
            <p>
              Harmony and resonance. Ideas and people that vibrate on the same frequency. Immediate collaborative sparks and shared trajectories.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item" style="display: block; opacity: 0.7;">
            <p class="knots-badge" style="color: var(--vibe-color);">LONG FORM</p>
            <strong style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              SPARs <span class="knots-badge" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--text-muted);">COMING SOON</span>
            </strong>
            <p>
              Friction and dialectic. Multi-player argumentation sessions combining Human and AI personas to stress-test reasoning.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="topic-item" style="display: block; opacity: 0.7;">
            <p class="knots-badge" style="color: var(--vibe-color);">SHORT/LONG FORM</p>
            <strong style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
              Voids <span class="knots-badge" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--text-muted);">COMING SOON</span>
            </strong>
            <p>
              The explicit absence of resonance. Immunological boundaries mapping where static, drifts, and vetoes severed the connection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="divider"><img src="/logo-h.svg" alt="ஃ" /></div>

      <section class="section--tight connect-section">
        <h2>The Operating Surface</h2><br />
        <p class="section-hook">
          Every engagement starts with a conversation. <br />Here is exactly how I operate.
        </p>

        <!-- Good Fit / Bad Fit -->
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
          <div style="background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.2); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
            <strong style="color: var(--body-color); display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">🟢 We are a good fit if:</strong>
            <ul style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; padding-left: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
              <li>You value deep architectural thinking over rapid, fragile execution.</li>
              <li>You are willing to look at the somatic friction in your organisation.</li>
              <li>You want an adversarial sparring partner, not a yes-man.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div style="background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
            <strong style="color: #e74c3c; display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">🔴 We are a bad fit if:</strong>
            <ul style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; padding-left: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
              <li>You want AI to execute tasks without declaring its reasoning intent.</li>
              <li>You view organisational culture as a machine rather than a living system.</li>
              <li>You are looking for "influencing" or polished corporate speak.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3 Collaboration Types -->
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">How We Can Work</h3>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
          <div class="dim-card" style="padding: 1rem; border-top: 3px solid var(--mind-color);">
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem;">1. Dialectic Strategy</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;">Multi-agent SPAR sessions designed to stress-test your core business logic.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dim-card" style="padding: 1rem; border-top: 3px solid var(--body-color);">
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem;">2. Architecture Build</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;">Encoding your tacit knowledge into high-fidelity agentic infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dim-card" style="padding: 1rem; border-top: 3px solid var(--soul-color);">
            <strong style="display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 0.95rem;">3. Friction Diagnostics</strong>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0;">Using the 108 KNOTS framework to unearth somatic toxicity in your teams.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 5 Conversation Prompts -->
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Start a Conversation</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Don't say "Hi." Hit me with one of these on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mnaveenriaz/" target="_blank" style="color: var(--accent);">LinkedIn</a>:</p>
        <ul style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; list-style-type: none; padding: 0;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>1.</strong> "Our agents keep hitting an ideological wall. Let's trace it back to the Claw."</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>2.</strong> "I think your SPAR methodology is flawed. Here is my thesis."</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>3.</strong> "We have a semantic drift problem in our organisation."</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>4.</strong> "Can you unpack the connection between Kural 486 and our deployment velocity?"</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>5.</strong> "I need an adversarial partner to break my new architecture."</li>
        </ul>

      </section>

      <TamilRoot
        tamil="ஒத்திசை"
        transliteration="Otticai"
        meaning="Harmony, resonance, being in tune. The frequency you emit when your mind, body, and soul are aligned."
        kural={`கடன்என்ப நல்லவை எல்லாம் கடன்அறிந்து\nசான்றாண்மை மேற்கொள் பவர்க்கு.`}
        kuralNumber={981}
        kuralTranslation="All virtues are said to be the duty of those who have embraced good conduct."
      />
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
